                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10128" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0634</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">396 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">代际冲突频发： S公司如何破解上下级沟通管理难题？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Intergenerational Conflicts on the Rise: How to Navigate Managerial Communication Challenges Between Hierarchies in S Company?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">马吟秋，赵曙明，马璨婧，童伟，李晋</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">马吟秋</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">超威半导体（上海）有限公司苏州工业园区分公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">代际员工；沟通冲突；沟通管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">generational employees; communication conflicts; communication management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着企业组织员工结构的不断迭代，代际员工因沟通差异所引发的纵向管理矛盾越发凸显，已成为企业组织治理中的重要挑战。本案例以S公司中层管理者张伟所面临的“上行沟通不畅”与“下行沟通失衡”典型双重困境为例，解析代际员工在沟通价值取向与行为模式层面存在的深层文化差异。通过剖析代际沟通冲突的行为特征，并以社会变迁为切入点，揭示中国社会从传统“熟人社会”向现代“陌生人社会”转型过程中，代际群体在沟通范式与权力地位认知方面所发生的结构性演变。针对上述问题，本案例创新性地构建了“合规管理与文化韧性”双轮驱动的有效沟通管理路径，旨在化解不同代际员工之间的沟通冲突。这一路径能够提升企业沟通治理效能，促进理论向实践的有效转化。本案例更有助于深化学生对企业沟通管理困境的理论认知，促进其在实践中提升沟通管理能力，培养兼具专业素养与理论深度的现代企业管理人才。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the continuous evolution of the employee structure in corporate organizations, vertical management conflicts caused by communication differences among intergenerational employees have become increasingly prominent, emerging as a key challenge in corporate governance. Taking the typical dual dilemmas of &quot;poor upward communication&quot; and &quot;imbalanced downward communication&quot; faced by Zhang Wei, a middle manager at Company S, as an example, this case analyzes the deep-seated cultural differences in communication values and behavioral patterns between intergenerational employees. By examining the behavioral characteristics of intergenerational communication conflicts and taking social changes as the entry point, it reveals the structural changes in communication paradigms and perceptions of power status among intergenerational groups during China&#39;s social transformation from the traditional &quot;acquaintance society&quot; to the modern &quot;stranger society&quot;. In response to the above issues, this case innovatively constructs an effective communication management path driven by the &quot;two wheels&quot; of &quot;compliance management and cultural resilience&quot;, aiming to resolve communication conflicts between employees of different generations. This path can enhance the effectiveness of corporate communication governance and promote the effective transformation of theory into practice. Furthermore, this case helps students deepen their theoretical understanding of the dilemmas in corporate communication management, improve their communication management capabilities in practice, and cultivate modern corporate management talents with both professional competence and theoretical depth.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理沟通》、《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">社会学理论；有效管理沟通理论；跨文化管理理论；合规管理理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10128" target="_blank">点击查看</a></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看案例使用说明</th>
